- Keyword: `#keyword/transformer`, `#keyword/attention`, `#keyword/machine-learning`, `#keyword/nlp`, `#keyword/factuality`, `#keyword/grounding`, `#keyword/evaluation`, `#keyword/benchmark`

## Social Media Hashtags
- Keep public hashtags separate from system tags (e.g., `#obsidian #zettelkasten`), and include only when requested by the user

## Assistant Rules
- When generating new notes, always include `#type/*` and at least one `#theme/*`
- Respect existing tag vocabulary; if a needed tag is missing, propose it explicitly before using
- Prefer adding tags as plain hashtags under a `Tags` section at the end

```markdown
---
# … note content …

---
Tags: #type/literature #theme/research #target/starterkit #keyword/machine-learning
```
